==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: hawksbill
<hw>hawks"bill`</hw></mhw>
<pr>(-b⟦icr⟧l`)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Zool.)</fld> <def>A sea turtle
(<spn>Eretmochelys imbricata</spn>), which yields the best quality of
tortoise shell; -- called also <altname>caret</altname>.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> hawksbill turtle, hawkbill, tortoiseshell turtle,
Eretmochelys imbricata.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Hawkbit</ent>⟦br⟧

